                },
                {
                  "@type": "Question",
                  "name": "Is Monel 400 material suitable for room temperature or high temperature?",
                  "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "Although Monel 400 can withstand certain high temperatures, its high-temperature resistance is limited. Therefore, Monel 400 is generally used in some room-temperature applications, typically marine vessels."
